{"tid":1534985,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全港警員委任證核查計劃","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:34:28.000Z","uid":222614,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4f70bbbca1485809d22148ada1e73be0285b9e","tid":1534985,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>全港警員委任證核查計劃</ins></span></div><br />\n鑑於近日有關警員執勤時無配帶委任證之投訴有所增加，市民若遇到懷疑冒警情況，可根據以下程序處理：<br />\n<br />\n1. Call 增援（人數最少為目標 4 倍）<br />\n1.1. 增援人數不足，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n1.2. 增援人數足夠，執行程序 2<br />\n2. 跟蹤<br />\n3. 等待增援到齊，及確保周圍環境安全，上前攔截<br />\n4. 向懷疑冒警人士表明理由，然後邀請對方去一個安靜既地方<br />\n4.1. 對方合作，則帶對方到一個安靜既地方，執行程序 5<br />\n4.2. 對方不合作，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>，及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n5. 要求對方出示委任證<br />\n5.1. 對方合作，出示委任證<br />\n5.1.1. 檢查並核實委任證<br />\n5.1.2. 委任證通過核實，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span> 及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n5.1.3. 委任證不通過核實，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>，及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n5.2. 對方不合作，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>，及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>. 影相，記錄身份及詳細資料（如適用）<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>. 使用適當武力，公民拘捕及／或合法禁固<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span>. 給予警告，然後命令對方離開<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>. 離開現場"},{"pid":"63475efe2e61539de485c3b6f59334f63bf9768f","tid":1534985,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"217ff134f8d64c2154ffe6d62232d5b6755ea6c2","tid":1534985,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"372f5e356a6c1fda19e882976be399e129c87bf7","tid":1534985,"uid":116793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b6569d1c5914c7e58287deb1e6218417031e7f3","tid":1534985,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a2feef636b4f477807e5cd915293e4307fd2b947","tid":1534985,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:48:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e83ca21accfd76803fe2322924ce7305b9475d4","tid":1534985,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4da1b5595b1387b6d3e4177ca4368128cb495708","tid":1534985,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"